metadata.name: Myriil Bijyre
metadata.description: Myriil Bijyre was once a human. Generated through a GAN - generative adversarial network, by mixing people who never existed with the ones who returned: a particularly vicious strain of world eating gods and daemons that recently came back to this plane. Now just a broken and corrupted soul, patiently waiting for a master or a mistress to obey to.
